# Keep the Vercel deploy archive small: upload only what the Next.js arcade build needs.
# The Godot games are served from Cloudflare R2 (Phoenix, Royal, Dragon), so their
# sources, raw art, and caches must NOT be bundled. Patterns are ANCHORED with a leading
# slash so they match ONLY the repo-root dirs — an unanchored `games/` would also match
# apps/arcade/public/games/ (the lobby thumbnails) and 404 them.
/games/
/Dragon-icons/
/slot-icons/
/fortune-wheel-assets/
/sharde-ui-kit/
/docs/
/Screenshot*.png
**/.godot/
**/.next/cache/
